Package: underwriter
Title: Automated Underwriting from Insurance Claim History
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Seokhoon", family = "Joo", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "seokhoonj@gmail.com")
Description: A data.table pipeline that cleanses insurance claim history,
    maps diagnosis codes to representative diseases, and decides each insured:
    standard products by matching a rule set of per-disease bands, and
    simplified-issue products by evaluating the three application-form questions.
    The engine is data-agnostic: rule sets, decision-code tables, and the
    simplified-issue workbook are supplied at run time, so it is not tied to any
    one insurer.
